casebody.data:
Johnny Jermaine MCMILLAN
v.
Harvey CLAY, Superintendent (Now referred to as Warden) of Lumberton Correctional Institution, State of North Carolina No. 316P18-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. July 11, 2019 Zachary Padget, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Johnny Jermaine McMillan, for McMillan, Johnny Jermaine. William R. West, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 10th of July 2019 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Cumberland County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th of July 2019."
